text: LaFayette ( ) is a city in, and the county seat of, Walker County, Georgia, United States. As of the 2020, the city's population was 6,888. It was founded as Chattooga. ==References== ==Other websites== * City of LaFayette * catwalkchatt.com The website for the Walker County Messenger, the county newspaper since 1877. * WQCH Radio Category:Cities in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:County seats in Georgia
